Text: "I belive in colours, scents, feelings and vibes.\nI belive in one humanity,\
  \ in hyman beings made of different colors and of the same material\nI belive the\
  \ material of human beings should be made of dreams, knowledge, curiosity and freedom\n\
  I belive freedom is the key to happyness\nand I belive happyness is the secret of\
  \ life \nbecouse life is beautiful.\nI want to discover and learn colors, scents,\
  \ tastes in my travels, to discover coltures an history, to learn different traditions.\
  \ I want to eat traditional food, speak with different people and enjoy life"
